"title": "8750: false teachings",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8750",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture repeatedly warns against false teachings, which deny or distort some aspect of the gospel. The origin of such teachings is attributed either to human error or to demonic inspiration.</p>\n<h2>Examples of false teachings</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:14-Rev2:15\">REV 2:14–2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:19\">MAT 5:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:1-2Thess2:2\">2TH 2:1–2:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1-1Tim4:3\">1TI 4:1–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20\">REV 2:20</a></p>\n<h2>Qualities of false teachings</h2>\n<h3>They are valueless</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt15:9\">MAT 15:9</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark7:7\">MRK 7:7</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa29:13\">ISA 29:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph5:6\">EPH 5:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:20-Col2:23\">COL 2:20–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3-1Tim1:7\">1TI 1:3–1:7</a></p>\n<h3>They are destructive in their nature</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:1\">2PE 2:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15\">MAT 7:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:29-Acts20:30\">ACT 20:29–20:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus1:10-Titus1:11\">TIT 1:10–1:11</a></p>\n<h3>They have the capacity to lead people astray</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts20:30\">ACT 20:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:14\">EPH 4:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:20-1Tim6:21\">1TI 6:20–6:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb13:9\">HEB 13:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:14-2Pet2:15\">2PE 2:14–2:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:26\">1JN 2:26</a></p>\n<h3>They may be popular</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:2\">2PE 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:4-Matt24:5\">MAT 24:4–24:5</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:5-Mark13:6\">MRK 13:5–13:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:3\">2TI 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:18-2Pet2:19\">2PE 2:18–2:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1-1John4:5\">1JN 4:1–4:5</a></p>\n<h3>They may be accompanied by miraculous signs</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:24\">MAT 24:24</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:22\">MRK 13:22</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:9-2Thess2:10\">2TH 2:9–2:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev13:11-Rev13:15\">REV 13:11–13:15</a></p>\n<h2>The origin of false teachings</h2>\n<h3>Demonic inspiration</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:1-1Tim4:2\">1TI 4:1–4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:3-2Cor11:4\">2CO 11:3–11:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:1-1John4:3\">1JN 4:1–4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev16:13-Rev16:14\">REV 16:13–16:14</a></p>\n<h3>Human error</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet2:3\">2PE 2:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col2:8\">COL 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:20-1Tim6:21\">1TI 6:20–6:21</a></p>\n<h2>Discerning false teachings</h2>\n<h3>By their content</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John4:2-1John4:3\">1JN 4:2–4:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor12:3\">1CO 12:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:20-1John2:23\">1JN 2:20–2:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:7-2John1:11\">2JN 1:7–1:11</a></p>\n<h3>By the teacher's lifestyle</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:15-Matt7:20\">MAT 7:15–7:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor11:20\">2CO 11:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:7-1John3:10\">1JN 3:7–3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:4\">JUD 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>By their effects</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:3-1Tim6:5\">1TI 6:3–6:5</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:3-1Tim1:4\">1TI 1:3–1:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim2:16-2Tim2:18\">2TI 2:16–2:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:20\">REV 2:20</a></p>\n<h2>The antidote to false teachings</h2>\n<h3>Holding fast to the true gospel</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:24\">1JN 2:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal1:6-Gal1:9\">GAL 1:6–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:18-1Tim1:20\">1TI 1:18–1:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:13-2Tim1:14\">2TI 1:13–1:14</a></p>\n<h3>Shunning false teachers</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom16:17-Rom16:18\">ROM 16:17–16:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim3:1-2Tim3:9\">2TI 3:1–3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Titus3:9-Titus3:11\">TIT 3:9–3:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2John1:9-2John1:11\">2JN 1:9–1:11</a></p>",
